	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm trying to generate interest in and gather feedback on a tool I've been working on for a while...
<br />
<br /><!-- w --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.nesicide.com">www.nesicide.com</a><!-- w -->
<br />
<br />Would you use it to create NES games?  What improvements would you need?  It doesn't yet have the following, but I hope to get to it someday:
<br />
<br />HELP files!
<br />Sound/music support
<br />Paint-style nametable creation
<br />
<br />Everything else is there in one form or other.  I have posted a few demo projects that I created, also.
<br />
<br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


