		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The project by itself seems promising.  I had a similar idea but still different but since I still have a lot of things to learn about the nes and my time is limited, I decided to focus on making a game first.
<br />
<br />I fiddled around a little bit with it and I have a few questions. First, how do you set a bank to be at a specific address or the size? Now they seems to be always at $8000. Depending on the mapper configuration, that will be important to be able to set it.
<br />
<br />Second, the project format is proprietary and only one file.  Is it possible to extract the data into independent files?
<br />
<br />I may have more comments once I play more with it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


