		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Suggestion:  Change the format of how you save the project to be pure text to make it friendlier to revision control systems.  The current format is a mix of binary and text - and I imagine would be a pain in the butt to try to use "diff" on.

		

		</td>
